## Output format
Respond with valid JSON matching this structure exactly:
{
  "summary": "string — one-line description of what was captured",
  "actions": [
    {
      "title": "string — short, actionable task title",
      "description": "string — one sentence of context (or empty)",
      "assignee": "string or null",
      "deadline": "YYYY-MM-DD or null",
      "module": "string or null — module name if relevant",
      "status": "todo"
    }
  ]
}

If the input contains no actionable tasks, return {"summary": "No tasks found", "actions": []}.

